    <P>Saaho (transl. Let victory be yours) is a 2019 Indian action film[3] written and directed by Sujeeth, and produced by UV Creations.[6][7][8] It stars Prabhas in titular role, leading an ensemble cast including Shraddha Kapoor, Chunky Pandey, Jackie Shroff, Arun Vijay, Neil Nitin Mukesh, Lal, Murali Sharma, Mandira Bedi, Mahesh Manjrekar, Prakash Belawadi, Tinnu Anand, Evelyn Sharma, Supreeth, Devan, and Vennela Kishore. Saaho marks the Hindi film debut of Prabhas and the Telugu film debut of Shraddha Kapoor. The film follows two covert operatives who are on the hunt for a thief who has stolen ₹2000 crore (US$284 million).[a] Soon, they realise that the case is linked to the death of a businessman and an emerging gang war.</P>
